  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that <a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\">House Templeton</a> may be distantly related to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> through <a href=\"/index.php/Jocelyn_Stark\" title=\"Jocelyn Stark\">Jocelyn Stark</a>, a sister of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>'s grandfather, <a href=\"/index.php/Edwyle_Stark\" title=\"Edwyle Stark\">Edwyle</a>?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, Catelyn V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403141700\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 80/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 420/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/209715